#10. Create a subquery in the WHERE clause that retrieves all unique hometeam_id values from the match table.
Select the team_long_name and team_short_name from the team table. Exclude all values from the subquery in the main query
-------------------------------------------------------------------
SELECT 
	-- Select the team long and short names
	team_long_name,
	team_short_name
FROM team
-- Exclude all values from the subquery
WHERE team_api_id NOT IN
     (SELECT DISTINCT hometeam_id FROM match);


